poisoning after participating in a feast in India's Rajasthan
state on Sunday, the Press Trust of India reported today.
</P>
<P>
All victims were rushed to hospital, official sources said,
adding that four of them were stated to be in critical condition.
</P>
<P>
The sources said that the guests started vomiting after taking
the meal.
</P>
<P>
Samples of food served at the feast had been taken for chemical
analysis to ascertain the cause of the poisoning, they added.
</P>
</TEXT>
