surrender, but the number of rebels supporting surrender
are increasing, Odok added.
</P>
<P>
IRA is under pressure from Ugandan army and is suffering from
the lack of food, the paper said.
</P>
<P>
IRA with 400 rebels is operating in northern Uganda from its
bases in southern Sudan. 
