phases of locating the vehicles emitting smoke," Makhdum said.
"There should be measures to correct them."
</P>
<P>
EPA Director General Asif Shuja said on the occasion that the
government had decided to start the clean environment campaign in
the entire country.
</P>
<P>
The present campaign in Islamabad was being launched as Pilot
Project, which will be replicated in the big cities after its
revaluation and consequent improvements, he said.  
