<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, August 4 (Xinhua) -- Nineteen suspected being in
unlawful possession of bhang (a kind of indian marijuana), illicit
brew (gongo) and some pellets of drugs will appear at a court in Dar
es Salaam today.
</P>
<P>
The local newspaper Daily News quoted the Regional Police
Commander, Alfred Gewe as saying that the suspects, including three
women, were arrested between July 17 and August 2 in various parts of
the city in the on-going police swoop.
</P>
